{"tid":1249260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【失威】法乙兵寧去德甲 拒加盟阿仙奴","createTime":"2019-06-21T16:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T10:45:15.000Z","uid":173952,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"16560a930b82bcebc2f3f1d18dd1921888c4784a","tid":1249260,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴增兵又再碰壁！法乙羅連安特翼鋒哥迪梅里斯 ( Alexis Claude-Maurice ) 表示無意加盟「兵工廠」，並希望轉投德甲球隊慕遜加柏，可見阿仙奴對球員的吸引力已經大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n根據外國傳媒報道，阿仙奴早前相中羅連安特翼鋒哥迪梅里斯，這位 21 歲攻擊球員今季於法乙攻入 14 球，阿仙奴曾出價 1,400 萬鎊求購，不但被羅連安特拒絕，哥迪梅里斯也表明自己希望加盟慕遜加柏，大讚對方是一支重視年輕球員的球會，並喜歡其計劃，認為十分適合自己。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n除了哥迪梅里斯外，阿仙奴亦一直追逐聖伊天的 18 歲後衛沙利巴 ( William Saliba ) ，據報聖伊天為球員標價 2,600 萬鎊，如果收購成功，阿仙奴將會花掉超過一半轉會預算。"},{"pid":"b9b5a4cdc6775faa76e98d1b245227fec2bd8ee1","tid":1249260,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"呢兩件都係FIFA 妖人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e64a308e55376c804185d7f312065db74df1a35","tid":1249260,"uid":19847,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"真係唔好嚟<br />\n嚟阿狗悔恨終生"},{"pid":"2df1cea38421e661381afe09340a038e90a208d4","tid":1249260,"uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1e64a308e55376c804185d7f312065db74df1a35","tid":1249260,"uid":19847,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"真係唔好嚟<br />\n嚟阿狗悔恨終生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"黎一黎就走咪可以"},{"pid":"ba6ba9858791ce2313a00bf83d09b1dd3c754eaa","tid":1249260,"uid":30476,"like":3,"disl